categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Giktoo Nelmo was a female Lurmen Jedi Master of the Jedi Order during the High Republic Era. When the Jedi Cohmac Vitus and Orla Jareni brought back four statues which appeared to be dark side artifacts, Nelmo led a ritual in the Shrine in the Depths intended to purify the statues.
